### System Time - Get Current Time
GET http://localhost:3000/system/time
Content-Type: application/json

###

### System Time - Get Offset (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:3000/system/time/offset
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

###

### System Time - Advance by 1 Hour (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "hours",
  "amount": 1
}

###

### System Time - Advance by 30 Minutes (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "minutes",
  "amount": 30
}

###

### System Time - Advance by 2.5 Hours (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "hours",
  "amount": 2.5
}

###

### System Time - Advance by 45 Minutes (Admin Only)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "minutes",
  "amount": 45
}

###

### System Time - Invalid Request (should fail - unit must be hours or minutes)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "days",
  "amount": 1
}

###

### System Time - Invalid Request (should fail - amount must be positive)
POST http://localhost:3000/system/time/advance
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "unit": "hours",
  "amount": -1
}

###
